    <note>Zhang(1) Qixian [183] His family moved to Luoyang when he was 3 because of disorder during the Five Dynasties. Zonghui's [305] and Zongjian's [3167] father, Zigao's [7171] grandfather. Father-in-law of Wang(2) Juzheng's [8145] brother, Jushan [3945]. Jushan's son-in-law was Sheng(1) Du's [8109] elder cousin Jing's [3739] son, Zunfu [3743]. Zhang(1) Zongjian was Wang(2) Shu(1)'s [1877] son-in-law. XCB, 24.4a-5a; SHY:SH, 49.5a; SS, 265.15a-18a. CB, 3, 2420-21.</note>
